{"id":116501,"date":[{"year":1946,"month":10,"day":13}],"page":"7","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"世纪风","column":"","genre":"","count":"444","ytitle":"","mtitle":"猫头鹰","ftitle":"","authors":["陈伟"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈伟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终朝躲进阴郁的山林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渴望着董事的露滴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他:希特勒一样的眼睛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"墨沙里尼一像的脸嘴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"费朗哥一样的心肺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我咒诅他——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个禽类的妖孽；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他歌颂夜的神秘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地拥护黑暗的暴力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它增恨日月星辰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它厌恶灯辉和闪电，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"究竟为什么荒淫如许?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我咒诅他——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这固禽类的妖孽!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在家时，母亲曾经"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"编织一个恐怖的故事:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说它是阎王的传令兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开口唱歌便是催命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老年人简直听不得，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——原来外祖父的死，就因被他"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“逐”去了“魂”灵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我只当这是撕谎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今可知道了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——我正亲眼着到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他吞噬同类以肥已，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“弱肉强食”是他所强调的千古"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不移的“天演公例”；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“四海皆兄弟”，他何曾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相信这个真理?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊!可怜的失眠人呀!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天的温暖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远流不进你的梦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今夜，当你不止一次地听到它幽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灵似的呼唤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你那古井样的心田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可曾激起几朵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪花的细沫吗?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万不要悲哀，还是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"提起嗓子跟我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱一支热血歌吧:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"……黑暗快要收了，光明已经射"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到古罗马的城头!……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊:我们的脉络朝着太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马上就得舒展了；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听吧，那雄鸡的号角"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越来越响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看他这个妖孽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有什么鬼花样:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九四六·九·二八改稿"}]}